    "comment_zh": "取得共享特征图的通道宽度。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        anchor_generator = AnchorGenerator(",
    "comment_zh": "为 RPN 创建多尺度锚框生成器。"
   },
   {
    "code": "            sizes=((32, 64, 128, 256, 512),),",
    "comment_zh": "设置覆盖小到大目标的锚框尺寸。"
   },
   {
    "code": "            aspect_ratios=((0.5, 1.0, 2.0),)",
    "comment_zh": "设置常见的宽高比。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        )",
    "comment_zh": "结束锚框生成器配置。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        rpn_head = RPNHead(out_channels, anchor_generator.num_anchors_per_location()[0])",
    "comment_zh": "RPN 为每个位置预测目标性和框偏移。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        roi_pooler = MultiScaleRoIAlign(",
    "comment_zh": "创建从 FPN 多层取样的 RoIAlign。"
   },
   {
    "code": "            featmap_names=['0', '1', '2', '3'],",
    "comment_zh": "指定参与池化的多尺度特征层。"
   },
   {
    "code": "            output_size=7, sampling_ratio=2",
    "comment_zh": "把每个候选区域变为 7×7 特征。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        )",
    "comment_zh": "结束 RoIAlign 配置。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        representation_size = 1024",
    "comment_zh": "设置框头隐藏表示维度。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        box_head = TwoMLPHead(out_channels * 7 * 7, representation_size)",
